<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's one of the world's most iconic models who has dominated leading fashion campaigns for decades.</p>

<p>And Kate Moss cut a radiant figure as she stepped out make-up free with boyfriend Count Nikolai von Bismarck in West London on Friday.</p>

<p>The catwalk Queen, 46, appeared relaxed as she stood on the street before hugging goodbye Dior &amp; Fendi creative director Kim Jones during the low-key outing.</p>

<p>Out and about: Kate Moss cut a radiant figure as she stepped out make-up free with boyfriend Count Nikolai von Bismarck in West London on Friday</p>

<p>Kate kept her look simple for the outing, opting for a white shirt worn beneath a black leather jacket.</p>

<p>The mother-of-one styled her blonde tresses in a simple centre-parting, while she let her natural beauty shine through by ditching her cosmetics for the day. </p>

<p>Kate appeared relaxed as she chatted to Kim, 47, and Nikolai, 33, outside after leaving what appeared to be a photoshoot.</p>

<p>She then gripped on her her smartly-dressed beau's arm before they headed down the street together.  </p>

<p>Pals: The catwalk Queen, 46, appeared relaxed as she stood on the street before hugging goodbye Dior &amp; Fendi creative director Kim Jones during the low-key louting</p>

<p>The fashion star recently returned to London after she had been isolating in her Cotswolds mansion with her daughter Lila, 17, alongside Kate's long-term partner Count Nikolai von Bismarck, 33, and her half-sister Lottie, 22.</p>

<p>The group were also joined by Kate's hairdresser friend James Brown.</p>

<p>A source told MailOnline: 'Kate and James have been friends their entire careers, they're like family. They're very comfortable living together.</p>

<p>'It's an added perk that James is a hairdresser and has been able to lend his hand when it comes to overgrown roots and out of control hair.</p>

<p>Style: Kate kept her look simple for the outing, opting for a white shirt worn beneath a black leather jacket</p>

<p>'Lottie, who's dyed her hair pink in lockdown, has also formed a close bond with James – and regularly shops with him when getting food for the house.'</p>

<p>The blonde has been sober for two years as she maintains a healthy lifestyle following decades of partying.</p>

<p>Kate was once known for her wild ways, but her longtime friend, DJ Fat Tony, has revealed she is now clean, with the pair having more fun now than ever before.</p>

<p>Off they go: She then gripped on her her smartly-dressed beau's arm before they headed down the street together</p>

<p>Her producer pal, 54 - who himself has been sober for 13 years - said in a new interview: 'Kate's been clean for over two years. Me and my sober mates now have a better time than we ever did when we used to drink and take drugs.'</p>

<p>Kate recently admitted she's tried to cut down on caffeine and nicotine, and enjoys having more quiet nights in.</p>

<p>Speaking to NBC's Megyn Kelly, the style icon revealed: 'I go to bed, I drink lots of water, not too much coffee, and I'm trying to cut down on cigarettes.'</p>

<p>Close: The blonde's longtime friend, DJ Fat Tony (pictured in 2019), recently revealed she has been sober for over two years, with the pair having more fun now than ever before</p>
